The paper proposes a generative adversarial network (GAN) approach for predicting desirable 3D dose distributions in radiation therapy treatment planning. This involves automated prediction of treatment plans, which is a task that falls under the categories of computer vision (cs.CV), machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural networks (cs.NE), and signal processing (cs.SI). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
